    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats are supple and completely free of wear or creasing. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, meticulously documented service history and strictly garage-kept storage. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
      "price": 48500.0,
