    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a pristine, original interior. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superior, it offers the performance and aesthetic appeal of a brand-new acquisition. A definitive choice for the sophisticated buyer seeking excellence without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
