    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve totally babied this car, kept it tucked away in the garage, and made sure it stayed sparkling clean inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
